//  shrub      | #                                     | deciduous         | leptophyll    | low                     | extremely cold                    | annual        | low              | very low                | low                     | infertile                  | #                                          | #                                   | #                                   | PyricTussockSavanna        ,
//  herbaceous | #                                     | deciduous         | leptophyll    | low                     | extremely cold                    | annual        | low              | very low                | low                     | infertile                  | #                                          | #                                   | #                                   | PyricTussockSavanna        ,
//  bare       | #                                     | deciduous         | leptophyll    | low                     | extremely cold                    | annual        | low              | very low                | low                     | infertile                  | #                                          | #                                   | #                                   | PyricTussockSavanna        ,
//  tree       | low                                 | deciduous         | leptophyll    | low                     | extremely cold                    | annual        | low              | very low                | low                     | infertile                  | #                                          | #                                   | #                                   | HummockSavanna             ,
